<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Neural Gateway // LachlanM05</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Securely bridge your local AI hardware to the public web." />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="https://lachlanm05.com/ai/favicon.ico" /> <!-- in prod, make it /favicon.ico -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" /> <!-- in prod, make it /style.css -->
  
  <style>
    /* landing page specific overrides */
    .hero-btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        background: var(--accent);
        color: #000;
        font-weight: 700;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin-top: 20px;
        transition: transform 0.2s;
        border: none;
        text-decoration: none;
    }
    .hero-btn:hover { 
        transform: translateY(-2px); 
        box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(119, 170, 255, 0.4); 
    }
    
    .step-number {
        font-family: var(--mono);
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        display: block;
    }

    .vt-badge {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        padding: 6px 12px;
        background: rgba(121, 224, 143, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid var(--ok);
        color: var(--ok);
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-family: var(--mono);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        margin-top: 10px;
        transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .vt-badge:hover {
        background: rgba(121, 224, 143, 0.2);
    }

    .hero-image-container {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .hero-image {
        max-width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        max-height: 250px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.3));
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="wrap">
    <header>
      <div class="brand">
        <img 
        src="https://lachlanm05.com/ai/me.png" 
        alt="me" 
        style="width: 32px; height: 32px; object-fit: contain;">
        <span>LachlanM05</span>
      </div>
      <nav aria-label="Primary">
        <a href="https://lachlanm05.com">Main Site</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/LachlanM05" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
        <% if (user) { %>
            <a href="/dashboard" style="color: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent);">Dashboard</a>
        <% } else { %>
            <a href="/login">Login</a>
        <% } %>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero" id="about">
      
      <article class="card">
        
        <h1 style="margin-top: 15px;">Expose your local GPU to the web. Securely.</h1>
        
        <p class="muted" style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6;">
          A reverse WebSocket tunnel that bridges your local Ollama instance to a public API endpoint. 
          No port forwarding. No price. Always.
        </p>

        <div class="badges" style="margin: 20px 0;">
          <span class="badge">Windows Client /</span>
          <span class="badge">OpenAI Compatible /</span>
          <span class="badge">End-to-End Tunnel</span>
        </div>
        
        <div style="margin-top: 30px;">
            <a href="/register" class="hero-btn">Get Started</a>
            <a href="#setup" style="margin-left: 20px; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.9rem;">Read the Guide ‚Üì</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <aside class="card" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
        
        <div class="hero-image-container">
            <img src="https://lachlanm05.com/ai/logo.png" alt="Mascot" class="hero-image"> 
        </div>

        <div style="flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;">
            <div class="kicker">Security Report</div>
            <h3 style="margin-bottom: 5px;">Client Safety</h3>
            <p class="muted" style="font-size: 0.85rem;">
              The client is an unsigned Electron executable. I believe in transparency.
            </p>
            
            <div style="margin-top: 15px;">
                <div class="kicker" style="font-size: 0.7rem;">VirusTotal Scan (v1.0.1)</div>
                <a href="https://www.virustotal.com/gui/file/dd213c886f91c6cd15c8a1f593654831af1c513976e4a5f3efe61d27a82db024/detection" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none;">
                    <div class="vt-badge">
                        <span>üõ°Ô∏è 0/71 Detections</span>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
            <p class="muted" style="font-size: 0.7rem; margin-top: 10px; opacity: 0.6;">
                *Windows Smartscreen might warn you, as I can't afford a signing cert. This detection will be updated within 5 minutes of each update that is pushed.
            </p>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <section class="grid">
      <div class="tile" style="grid-column: span 12">
        <div class="kicker">How?</div>
        <div class="projects" style="margin-top: 20px;">
            <article class="project">
                <h3>1. The Gateway</h3>
                <p class="muted">A public Node.js server that acts as the entry point. It authenticates requests and routes traffic.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="project">
                <h3>2. The Tunnel</h3>
                <p class="muted">Your PC connects <i>outbound</i> via a WebSocket. No need to open router ports or mess with firewalls.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="project">
                <h3>3. The Hardware</h3>
                <p class="muted">Requests are executed on your local GPU via Ollama, and the text is streamed back instantly.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="project">
                <h3>4. Safety</h3>
                <p class="muted">Only IP's you permit will be able to send requests.</p>
            </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="setup" class="grid">
      <div class="tile" style="grid-column: span 8">
        <div class="kicker">Deployment Guide</div>
        <h2>How to Connect</h2>
        
        <div class="cardlist" style="margin-top: 20px;">
            <div class="listitem">
                <div>
                    <span class="step-number">01</span>
                    <strong>Create an Account</strong>
                    <p class="muted" style="margin:0;">Register on this dashboard to generate your API keys.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="/register" class="btn">Register</a>
            </div>

            <div class="listitem">
                <div>
                    <span class="step-number">02</span>
                    <strong>Download Client</strong>
                    <p class="muted" style="margin:0;">Download the <code>.exe</code> and install it on your PC running Ollama.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="https://lachlanm05.com/ai/LachlanAI Node Setup 1.0.1.exe" class="btn">Download</a>
            </div>

            <div class="listitem">
                <div>
                    <span class="step-number">03</span>
                    <strong>Link & Launch</strong>
                    <p class="muted" style="margin:0;">Copy your Slug and Key from the Dashboard into the App.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="listitem">
                <div>
                    <span class="step-number">04</span>
                    <strong>Copy 'n Paste</strong>
                    <p class="muted" style="margin:0;">Copy your Slug and Key from the Dashboard to the website you would like to use it on, and enjoy.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="listitem">
                <div>
                    <span class="step-number"></span>
                    <strong>Lost?</strong>
                    <p class="muted" style="margin:0;">Head over to <a href="https://discord.gg/4ARq2cBtSy">my discord</a> and into the Neural Gateway category for more info.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tile" style="grid-column: span 4">
        <div class="kicker">Open Source</div>
        <h2>Audit the Code</h2>
        <p class="muted">
            Don't trust the EXE and a inconspicuous virus total result? Good.
            <br><br>
            The entire stack is open source.
        </p>
        <div class="links" style="margin-top: 20px;">
            <a href="https://github.com/LachlanM05/neural-gateway" target="_blank">
                View Source on GitHub
            </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="footer-inner">
          <p>¬© 2026 LachlanM05 ‚Ä¢ Neural Gateway</p> 
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
